          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting Homeowners from Disaster Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill repeals the tax rule in effect through 2025 that limits the deduction for personal casualty losses to losses attributable to a federally declared disaster.</p>]]>
